ent_3794867" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3794867" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3794867" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Nancy-Moir-and-Jim-Moir-Photo-by-Mike-Marsland_Getty-Images-for-Sky-Arts-Awards-2024.jpg" alt="南希·莫伊尔和吉姆·莫伊尔在天空奖颁奖典礼上" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Nancy-Moir-and-Jim-Moir-Photo-by-Mike-Marsland_Getty-Images-for-Sky-Arts-Awards-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Nancy-Moir-and-Jim-Moir-Photo-by-Mike-Marsland_Getty-Images-for-Sky-Arts-Awards-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Nancy-Moir-and-Jim-Moir-Photo-by-Mike-Marsland_Getty-Images-for-Sky-Arts-Awards-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Nancy-Moir-and-Jim-Moir-Photo-by-Mike-Marsland_Getty-Images-for-Sky-Arts-Awards-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Nancy-Moir-and-Jim-Moir-Photo-by-Mike-Marsland_Getty-Images-for-Sky-Arts-Awards-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Nancy-Moir-and-Jim-Moir-Photo-by-Mike-Marsland_Getty-Images-for-Sky-Arts-Awards-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3794867" class="wp-caption-text">南希·莫伊尔 (Nancy Moir) 和吉姆·莫伊尔 (Jim Moir) 出席天空奖 — 图片来源：Mike Marsland/Getty Images for Sky Arts Awards 2024</figcaption></figure><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/vic-reeves-admits-he-never-really-speaks-to-comedy-partner-bob-mortimer-3428586">里夫斯去年承认，他“再也没有真正</a>和他的喜剧搭档<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bob-mortimer">鲍勃·莫蒂默</a>交谈过”。</p><p> 1986 年，两人组成了喜剧双人剧《Vic 和 Bob》，并以 90 年代的小组剧<em>《流星》</em>而闻名。里夫斯承认，他现在很少与莫蒂默联系。</p><p>他说：“我们从来没有真正说过太多话。鲍勃和我从来都不喜欢打电话。”他说。 “[我]会时不时地见到他，聊聊一些事情。”</p><p>近年来，里夫斯专注于绘画，并以真名发布他的作品。</p><p>在其他消息中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-darkness-announce-new-album-dreams-on-toast-and-2025-uk-tour-including-wembley-show-with-ash-3794787">The Darkness 刚刚公布了新专辑和巡演的细节</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/vic-reeves-invades-stage-during-the-darkness-set-at-sky-arts-awards-2024-3794849">维克·里夫斯 (Vic Reeves) 登上 2024 年天空艺术奖《黑暗》舞台后的场景</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
